item.title: Dewas: Collector Rishav Gupta reviews health department programmes
item.description: Dewas: Collector Rishav Gupta reviews health department programmes Dewas (Madhya Pradesh): The collector of Dewas, Rishav Gupta reviewed various health programmes run by the health department in the collectorate's office hall.
